#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.quantile.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.quantile"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.dataframe_quantile:1 of
msgid "Return values at the given quantile over requested axis."
msgstr "返回在给定分位数上的值，按请求的轴进行计算。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.dataframe_quantile of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.dataframe_quantile:3 of
msgid "Value between 0 <= q <= 1, the quantile(s) to compute."
msgstr "介于 0 <= q <= 1 之间的值，表示要计算的分位数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.dataframe_quantile:5 of
msgid "Equals 0 or 'index' for row-wise, 1 or 'columns' for column-wise."
msgstr "等于 0 或 'index' 表示按行计算，1 或 'columns' 表示按列计算。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.dataframe_quantile:7 of
msgid ""
"If False, the quantile of datetime and timedelta data will be computed as"
" well."
msgstr "如果为 False，datetime 和 timedelta 数据的分位数也会被计算。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.statistics.quantile.dataframe_quantile:10 of
msgid ""
"This optional parameter specifies the interpolation method to use, when "
"the desired quantile lies between two data points `i` and `j`: * linear: "
"`i + (j - i) * fraction`, where `fraction` is the   fractional part of "
"the index surrounded by `i` and `j`. * lower: `i`. * higher: `j`. * "
"nearest: `i` or `j` whichever is nearest. * midpoint: (`i` + `j`) / 2."
msgstr ""
"此可选参数指定当所需分位数位于两个数据点 `i` 和 `j` 之间时使用的插值方法"
"：* linear: `i + (j - i) * fraction`，其中 `fraction` 是 `i` 和 `j` 之间"
"的索引的小数部分。* lower: `i`。* higher: `j`。* nearest: 离得最近的 `i` "
"或 `j`。* midpoint: (`i` + `j`) / 2。"

